@{"   AddCommand   " link "AddCmd" 0}  @{"     Expand     " link "Expand" 0}  @{"      Pack      " link "Pack" 0}  @{"   SetPattern   " link "SetPattern" 0}
@{" AddKeyCommand  " link "AddKeyCmd" 0}  @{"     Extern     " link "Extern" 0}  @{"     Parent     " link "Parent" 0}  @{"      SetX      " link "SetX" 0}
@{" AddMenuCommand " link "AddMenuCmd" 0}  @{"    Filestat    " link "Filestat" 0}  @{"      Pens      " link "Pens" 0}  @{"     Single     " link "Single" 0}
@{"    Archive     " link "Archive" 0}  @{"      Find      " link "Find" 0}  @{"    PrintDir    " link "PrintDir" 0}  @{"      Sort      " link "Sort" 0}
@{"      Auto      " link "Auto" 0}  @{"      Font      " link "Font" 0}  @{"    Protect     " link "Protect" 0}  @{"     Status     " link "Status" 0}
@{"   BarFormat    " link "BarFormat" 0}  @{"   GetHistory   " link "GetHistory" 0}  @{"     Quiet      " link "Quiet" 0}  @{"     StdIO      " link "StdIO" 0}
@{"     Batch      " link "Batch" 0}  @{"      GUI       " link "GUI" 0}  @{"      Quit      " link "Quit" 0}  @{"      Swap      " link "Swap" 0}
@{"     Button     " link "Button" 0}  @{"   HostScreen   " link "HostScreen" 0}  @{"      Read      " link "Read" 0}  @{"   Swapselect   " link "Swapselect" 0}
@{" ChangeCommand  " link "ChgCmd" 0}  @{"    HideDev     " link "HideDev" 0}  @{"   Recursion    " link "Recursion" 0}  @{"  TitleFormat   " link "TitleFormat" 0}
@{"     Check      " link "Check" 0}  @{"      Icon      " link "Icon" 0}  @{"     Rename     " link "Rename" 0}  @{"     UnLock     " link "UnLock" 0}
@{"     Choose     " link "Choose" 0}  @{"    Iconify     " link "Iconify" 0}  @{"     Reset      " link "Reset" 0}  @{"     UnMark     " link "UnMark" 0}
@{"  CloseWindow   " link "CloseWindow" 0}  @{"      Info      " link "Info" 0}  @{"   ReqPattern   " link "ReqPattern" 0}  @{"     Unpack     " link "Unpack" 0}
@{"     Color      " link "Color" 0}  @{"      Last      " link "Last" 0}  @{"      REXX      " link "REXX" 0}  @{"      View      " link "View" 0}
@{"    Comment     " link "Comment" 0}  @{"   LoadConfig   " link "Batch" 0}  @{"      Root      " link "Root" 0}  @{"      Wait      " link "Wait" 0}
@{"    Confirm     " link "Confirm" 0}  @{"      Lock      " link "Lock" 0}  @{"   SaveConfig   " link "SaveConfig" 0}  @{"     Window     " link "Window" 0}
@{"      Copy      " link "Copy" 0}  @{"    Makedir     " link "Makedir" 0}  @{"    ScrBack     " link "ScrBack" 0}  @{"    WinInfo     " link "WinInfo" 0}
@{"     Delete     " link "Delete" 0}  @{"      Move      " link "Move" 0}  @{"    ScrFront    " link "ScrFront" 0}
@{"    Deselect    " link "Deselect" 0}  @{"      Msg       " link "Msg" 0}  @{"     Select     " link "Select" 0}
@{"    DevList     " link "DevList" 0}  @{"     NewDir     " link "NewDir" 0}  @{"    SetDate     " link "SetDate" 0}

@{"Removed Functions" link "removed" 0}
@endnode
@node "Install" "Really no joke..."
@REMARK .4
@{b}-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
                         How to install DiskMaster2
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------@{ub}

This is one of the simplest things on earth, so I won`t spend any time on
writing a special installer script.

1. Copy DiskMaster2 and DiskMaster2.info to your favourite "Tools" directory using
   the Workbench or DiskMaster2 itself.
2. Copy DiskMaster2.guide to any directory of your choice.
3. If you like, copy the ARexx scripts from DiskMaster2/rexx to Sys:Rexx
   and the tools from ../c to Sys:C

That`s it!

Additional steps:

1. Start DiskMaster2 and select "Save Config" from the "Project" menu.
2. *READ* this guide and use a text-editor to customize your Startup.DM.
   The file "MyStartup.DM" may give you additional ideas.
3. Copy the appropriate DM2.catalog to Sys:Locale/catalogs/<your language>
   or to the same dir you have copied DM2 to.
@endnode
